Pork Chops with Applesauce

30 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

PaleoGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyComfort FoodQuick Cooking

Description

Juicy pork chops paired with sweet applesauce for a delightful meal that's easy to make.

Ingredients

  • pork chops: 2 pieces
  • applesauce: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • onion powder: 1 teaspoon
